  * * * * * * * *     ZOOM ISPF/PDF EDIT command      * * * * * * * *
  * * * * * * * *                                     * * * * * * * *
  * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *

  Function :   By placing the cursor on a JCL card containing an EXEC
  ----------   statement, and issueing the ZOOM command, this Edit
               macro will "zoom in" on (display in browse) the JCL
               PROC featured on the statement.

  Command syntax : ZOOM
  ---------------- ZOOM HELP or H

  Note :        This command is most useful when defined to a PF key,
  ------        thus leaving the cursor free to move to the line
                containing the EXEC statement.
